{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5931b1b055","title":"“可用教授团来治校”","origin":"北京地质勘探学院党委会宣传部编《社会主义教育参考资料第二编：右派言论汇编》，1957年10月5日。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"66a09b09ad","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"5931b1b055"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"03e4c76cc6","name":"苏宝贵"},{"id":"2286075d0d","name":"黄学玲"},{"id":"4912cadfa8","name":"王豪"},{"id":"4fac142a8e","name":"姚鸿烈"},{"id":"7d7fef83de","name":"华荫桐"},{"id":"82cc012e26","name":"北京地质勘探学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"cd9aec268c","type":"title","text":"“可用教授团来治校”","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"cee2a74c3d","type":"authors","text":"北京地质勘探学院苏宝贵姚鸿烈黄学玲华荫桐王豪","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"c8cec6b39f","type":"paragraph","text":"苏宝贵说：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"ae7e64af00","type":"paragraph","text":"「党委可以取消，可用教授团来治校，党委不熟悉业务。」","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"bd8da3beea","type":"paragraph","text":"姚鸿烈说：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"5891c95188","type":"paragraph","text":"「党不能领导高等学校，党不懂学术，党委连二分之一加三分之一都不知道，只能去领导中小学。」","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"272817fd3b","type":"paragraph","text":"黄学玲说：","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"f3e890c3bc","type":"paragraph","text":"「党委包办一切，独断独行，党委制是否能发挥大家的才能和积极性，党委对地质事业很不熟悉，不能胜任领导。党委不能把领导土改等的经验搬到学校。」","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"155e887aa3","type":"paragraph","text":"华荫桐说：","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"cbcd083add","type":"paragraph","text":"「党委是害人的。」","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"b822223970","type":"paragraph","text":"「再过几十年，党就要发生危机。」","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"6d2004f80f","type":"paragraph","text":"「根据现在的材料，有足够的理由不相信党委，撤消他们的领导。」","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"d93b404c38","type":"paragraph","text":"王豪说：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"3fe723fd13","type":"paragraph","text":"「在我思想上的教授治校就是业务、学术、科研和学校的大政方针，上面在高教部领导下，学校内由教授会议来决定。党委都参加到教授会议之内，此外并有对教授会议及全校进行思想上的领导与组织上的监督，如有原则性的错误，则进行不调和的斗争。党委治校在以前是必须的，这就相当于初解放时军事管制。如果现在还不放手与高级知识份子，就说明仍然对他们不信任。」","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"},{"id":"df02ab42e9","type":"paragraph","text":"「党委放心吧！不要对高级知识分子的思想估计过低。何况现在青年学生都有很高的觉悟，党又在思想上领导与组织上监督呢？」","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055"}],"page":{"id":"67a9eb70e6","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5931b1b055","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}